POSIX-RT-SharedMem

POSIX::RT::SharedMem is a module for using posix shared memory. See the perldoc for more information on how to do this.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc POSIX::RT::SharedMem

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=POSIX-RT-SharedMem

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/POSIX-RT-SharedMem

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/POSIX-RT-SharedMem

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/POSIX-RT-SharedMem


